==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Chirp
<hw>Chirp</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A short, sharp note, as of a bird or
insect.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧The <qex>chirp</qex> of flitting bird.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Bryant.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

